===Noun===
'''cotton''' ([[uncountable]])

#A plant that encases its [[seed]] in a thin [[fiber]] that is harvested and used as a [[fabric]] or [[cloth]].
# The [[textile]] that is [[harvest]]ed from the cotton [[plant]].


====Etymology====
from an arabic word "cotn" which has the same meaning


